{"id":407716,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/52/95/529577.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"<a href=\"https://chii.in/group/topic/407644\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">前情提要</a><br><br>我超喜欢我的房间的。<br><br>——————<br>小猫越来越可爱了，这两天已经可以到处爬了。<br><img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/926e7525076662347446344540c0106b476799321.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1tfyTYQE49\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">满月小猫</a><br><br>今天给房间加装了俩根灯管，36w的可调色照明灯，果然房间亮堂起来了心情也会跟着好起来，阴沉的房间虽然很有安全感，但人也会变得阴暗沉寂，亮堂起来真舒服啊。<br><br>买的俩灯管得查俩插头，又分别用俩不同的开关控制，变色又得连续开关三次才能从白炽切换成舒服的混合暖色，很麻烦。<br><img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/b03b7c18d5dbe8e9b06408b4e762f2b1476799321.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/1f84032f2ea46842a3185a8582d23aa3476799321.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>于是我拿小刀切断了其中一个插头，再把俩条线的零火线都割开分别重新串联连接，最后用电工胶布缠好，一次成功了，现在控制这俩灯管只需要一个插头和一个开关了。<br><img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/f9778e78589c2de359f8f5b857c91881476799321.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/ab25d32d8ef247fe578fcbd9a142936a476799321.jpg@1052w_!web-dynamic.avif\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br>不是很难，但自己动手非常有乐趣。<br><br>买了一台新的显示器，替代有一台屏幕右下角背光坏了一块儿的一台，等调试完了我就有四块屏幕同时工作了。<br><img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/c67bf3dd9fd88cae0abd23a7a9c7cb55476799321.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/d2268d140eb872b81ed24dc0bc5ba5fa476799321.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referr